<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8715] New Admin UI&apos;s Schema screen fails for fields with stored=false and indexed content</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8715</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In techproducts example, using new Admin UI and trying to load the Schema for text field causes blank screen and the Javascript error in the developer console:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Error: row.flags is undefined
getFieldProperties@http://localhost:8983/solr/js/angular/controllers/schema.js:482:40
$scope.refresh/&amp;lt;/&amp;lt;@http://localhost:8983/solr/js/angular/controllers/schema.js:76:38
....
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tested with 5.5rc3&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;mac, firefox&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
